Hello.
Using the  `/crm/v3/objects/contacts/search` api, is it possible to have the filters in filter groups be a logical OR operator instead of AND?
I have 8 keys which i need to check the value of, the value is the same for each filter, but i don't know which key it is on.
So from the example in the docs:
```"filterGroups":[{
      "filters": [
        {
          "propertyName": "firstname",
           "operator": "EQ",
            "value": "Alice"
        },
          {
            "propertyName": "lastname",
            "operator": "EQ",
            "value": "Smith"
          }]
]}```
Can i not have a result which is all contacts with firstname equals Alice, or lastname equals Smith?
